<p>
  The RAiD system has been updated to support the latest metadata standards,
  enabling richer descriptions of research activities and improved
  interoperability across institutions.
</p>
<p>
  This update aligns RAiD with the evolving requirements of international
  research infrastructure, making it easier for institutions to describe,
  discover, and connect research activities across systems.
</p>
<p>
  Key changes include support for additional contributor roles, expanded
  subject classifications, and improved alignment with Schema.org and DataCite
  metadata vocabularies.
</p>
